description:
This 2D chess game is designed for minimal device and storage requirements, so, it can stay for a long time in your device)). Also it is designed to deliver non frustrating, smooth experience. In Free Chess you can play against computer or against another human, either with time control or not. If you play against another human, you can choose to automate rotate board, for better co-playing with friends, or with your father in the evenings)). Also, this application collects detailed statistics, which later can be used to get insights, and see your performance chart. If you want, you can get help from chess engine, or if you did wrong move, you can undo it.

Enjoy this game, and get regularly updates with astonishing new features.

* Completely free
* Designed for minimal device requirements
* Minimalist interface design
* Powerful chess engine with many levels of complexity
* Play against computer
* Play against another human, either with board rotation or not
* Play with time control
* Get hint
* Get help in form of safe and unsafe moves
* Save detailed statistics with charts of your performance for each AI level
* More than one interface theme
* More than one language


!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Google Play Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Hasmin.FreeChess&amp;hl=en
